# L1-3: Single dielectric wall — Brewster angle verification
# Wall at x=2, lossless concrete (eps_r=5.24, sigma=0)
# Brewster angle: theta_B = arctan(sqrt(5.24)) = 66.2 deg
# Validates: |Gamma_TM|^2 -> 0 at Brewster angle
o wall
v 2.0 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 50.0
v 2.0 -50.0 50.0
vn -1.0 0.0 0.0
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
f 1//1 3//1 4//1
